Training features a slide show and in depth video explanations and tutorials along with a step by step demonstration video on the procedure process. A 40 question multiple choice quiz for assessment & and a follow up phone call to answer any questions.

Additionally you will gain access to our PRO Store, product discounts and our BB Glow support group.

BB Glow Australia certificate included.
The program covers a comprehensive overview of the Mesotherapy & BB Glow process and products. Including basic skin anatomy, BB Blush, BB Lips & more.

Included BB Glow Training Kit valued at over $1000 dollars including:
1 KRX photo pen
1 MTS prep set
100 repair creams
10 BB Glow ampoules
2 CC Blush
5 Booster ampoules
5 KRX Meso booster face masks
1 KRX Milk Enzyme cleanser

Don't want a kit? You can swap this for a $700 voucher to be redeemed in our PRO store!
